snippet.title: Atomfall Gameplay Overview - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Ben Fisher from Rebellion dug into the details of Atomfall, an FPS adventure set in 1950s Yorkshire in the wake of a nuclear disaster. Atomfall is coming to PC, PlayStation and Xbox in 2025. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow
